<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪看着窗外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面又阴又冷。但没有下雪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两周后就是圣诞节。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪希望是一个白色圣诞节。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她闭上眼睛，祈祷下雪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，莉琪。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她指着桌子上的纸盘和水彩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们应该是做手工。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了。” 莉琪说。她喜欢做手工。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师准备的活动都很有趣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要做圣诞花环。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿起一个闪闪发光的花环。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真漂亮。” 莉琪说，“我喜欢那个天使。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个是纸盘吗？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。我们要用纸盘、水彩、胶水和其他一些东西做花环。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿起一个袋子，“我有一些旧的圣诞装饰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们可以选择自己喜欢的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，对折纸盘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后在中间剪一个半圆。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“已经像个花环了。” 莉琪打开纸盘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在在花环上画画，用你喜欢的东西装饰。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师指着桌子上的装饰品说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要用这个。” 波比拿起一个纸铃铛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要用这个。” 贾森拿起一个纸烛台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！” 尼娜和莉琪同时看到了天使。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我的！” 她们同时伸手拿天使。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜，我真的很想要这个。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是，莉琪。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么问题吗？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜想用我的天使。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的天使？” 尼娜皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们应该分享吗？” 尼娜问雪莉老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们很聪明，一定会想到办法的。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“分享？” 莉琪说，“要怎么分享一个天使呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以把它剪成两半。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪很想哭。她可不想要半个天使。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>半个天使一点也不好看。她想要整个天使。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系。” 莉琪小声说，“给尼娜吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜拿走天使的时候，她看着其他地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，莉琪。” 雪莉老师说，“你很棒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪看到尼娜的花环放在地板上晾干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>花环看上去很不错。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请让天下雪吧。” 莉琪小声地对天使说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在等花环变干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿出铃铛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们一边摇铃铛一边唱圣诞歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快就到了回家的时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪，花环真可爱！” 莉琪的妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她和尼娜的妈妈正拿着花环。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪，快来看！” 尼娜突然大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪跑到窗边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她不敢相信自己的眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下雪了！她的愿望成真了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着尼娜的花环，默默地对天使说谢谢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她对尼娜说：“我们出去玩儿吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>